text: East Ledang, a gated residential community, is my favourite get away whenever we are in JB.  The relax feeling and lush landscaping will awaken your senses.  Great place if you need to unwind away from your bustling schedules.  Anjung mall is just outside for your grocery need.  A great place for semi retirement ;)
Peacefu & l greenery place. With man made fish pond.
